      <title>Dimitri, 16: “My style is a mix of the 80s, skate and punk. Of these three, the ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWSkroiAVhO/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656820979_18580828843036149_8806288826580125831_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDMwOTE1ODc0MjAyMjIyMg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=XI3cNSgg_kYQ7kNvwHqQ3rs&amp;_nc_oc=AdqLroB8hjAD-R2LjrwvJg3Scd2K-snSBlFvR5VekojPS7vBbUW8CIiHfZ5BBobbFJo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=q2B29LrdcDFN2hd4FE-H1Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy5PXgvQSN2nhcGP6QIUtNHrhP11rTS6DskrRiGfapDCQ&amp;oe=69CA1058" alt="Instagram billede fra @hellooks" /></p><p><strong>@hellooks</strong></p><p>Dimitri, 16: “My style is a mix of the 80s, skate and punk. Of these three, the 80s is the main source of inspiration. 80s heavy metal bands like Anthrax and Megadeth were stylish. There are many stylish skaters, a good example is Mark Gonzales. Now I’m wearing my uncle’s old flannel shirt and my father’s old jeans. I’ve customized them both.”<br/>
<br/>
10 June 2007, Kaivopuisto<br/>
<br/>
#hellooks #streetstyle #year2007 #helsinkistreetstyle #skaterstyle</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656820979_18580828843036149_8806288826580125831_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDMwOTE1ODc0MjAyMjIyMg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=XI3cNSgg_kYQ7kNvwHqQ3rs&amp;_nc_oc=AdqLroB8hjAD-R2LjrwvJg3Scd2K-snSBlFvR5VekojPS7vBbUW8CIiHfZ5BBobbFJo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=q2B29LrdcDFN2hd4FE-H1Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy5PXgvQSN2nhcGP6QIUtNHrhP11rTS6DskrRiGfapDCQ&amp;oe=69CA1058" alt="Instagram billede fra @hellooks" /></p><p><strong>@hellooks</strong></p><p>Dimitri, 16: “My style is a mix of the 80s, skate and punk. Of these three, the 80s is the main source of inspiration. 80s heavy metal bands like Anthrax and Megadeth were stylish. There are many stylish skaters, a good example is Mark Gonzales. Now I’m wearing my uncle’s old flannel shirt and my father’s old jeans. I’ve customized them both.”<br/>
<br/>
10 June 2007, Kaivopuisto<br/>
<br/>
#hellooks #streetstyle #year2007 #helsinkistreetstyle #skaterstyle</p>]]></content:encoded>
